OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few bright spells initially,
OL,6,Fbut becoming generally cloudy with a
OL,7,Ffew light showers possible, though
OL,8,Fmost places likely remaining dry.
OL,9,FSunnier spells may develop later in
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Winds generally light.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FPlenty of clear spells going
OL,13,Finto the evening and turning chilly.
OL,14,FCloudier conditions soon developing
OL,15,Fnear the coast and perhaps spreading
OL,16,Ffurther inland later in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
